content_vision: The other characters in the song are experienced clubbers. They have no nostalgia. They talk a lot about simple feelings. A man who wants sex and a lot. He says kinky things at the club, but in good taste. In the beginning, he wants to find a new love and eventually he finds it. He doesn't just want sex, he wants an emotional relationship.
